            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I'm very sure why this happens. It's because vim.glob simply translates regex `a | b` into `a + b`, which is incorrect, since it means *ordered choice* in PEG. Also check the discussion: https://github.com/neovim/neovim/discussions/29199",
